{
  "video_id": "3boKz0Exros",
  "title": "How to turn a group of strangers into a team | Amy Edmondson",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12864.0,
      "end_time": 15435.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s August 5, 2010."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16166.0,
      "end_time": 20281.0,
      "text": "A massive collapse at the San Jos√© Copper Mine in Northern Chile"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20305.0,
      "end_time": 26486.0,
      "text": "has left 33 men trapped half a mile -- that&#39;s two Empire State Buildings --"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 26510.0,
      "end_time": 29341.0,
      "text": "below some of the hardest rock in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 30522.0,
      "end_time": 35211.0,
      "text": "They will find their way to a small refuge designed for this purpose,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 35236.0,
      "end_time": 39315.0,
      "text": "where they will find intense heat, filth"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 39340.0,
      "end_time": 42301.0,
      "text": "and about enough food for two men for 10 days."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 43436.0,
      "end_time": 46904.0,
      "text": "Aboveground, it doesn&#39;t take long"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 46928.0,
      "end_time": 50830.0,
      "text": "for the experts to figure out that there is no solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 50560.0,
      "end_time": 56238.0,
      "text": "No drilling technology in the industry is capable of getting through rock"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 56262.0,
      "end_time": 58695.0,
      "text": "that hard and that deep"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 58719.0,
      "end_time": 61540.0,
      "text": "fast enough to save their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 62612.0,
      "end_time": 65663.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not exactly clear where the refuge is."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 66933.0,
      "end_time": 69245.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not even clear if the miners are alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 70593.0,
      "end_time": 72605.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not even clear who&#39;s in charge."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 72629.0,
      "end_time": 78554.0,
      "text": "Yet, within 70 days, all 33 of these men will be brought to the surface alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 79900.0,
      "end_time": 82700.0,
      "text": "This remarkable story is a case study"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 82724.0,
      "end_time": 84830.0,
      "text": "in the power of teaming."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 84678.0,
      "end_time": 86170.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s \"teaming\"?"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 86410.0,
      "end_time": 88247.0,
      "text": "Teaming is teamwork on the fly."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 88272.0,
      "end_time": 90724.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s coordinating and collaborating with people"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 90748.0,
      "end_time": 92713.0,
      "text": "across boundaries of all kinds --"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 92737.0,
      "end_time": 97420.0,
      "text": "expertise, distance, time zone, you name it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 97445.0,
      "end_time": 99184.0,
      "text": "to get work done."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 99209.0,
      "end_time": 102784.0,
      "text": "Think of your favorite sports team, because this is different."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 102808.0,
      "end_time": 107793.0,
      "text": "Sports teams work together: that magic, those game-saving plays."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 107817.0,
      "end_time": 111899.0,
      "text": "Now, sports teams win because they practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 111924.0,
      "end_time": 116389.0,
      "text": "But you can only practice if you have the same members over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 116413.0,
      "end_time": 118529.0,
      "text": "And so you can think of teaming ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 118553.0,
      "end_time": 121843.0,
      "text": "Sports teams embody the definition of a team,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 121867.0,
      "end_time": 123236.0,
      "text": "the formal definition."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 123260.0,
      "end_time": 127261.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a stable, bounded, reasonably small group of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 127285.0,
      "end_time": 129966.0,
      "text": "who are interdependent in achieving a shared outcome."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 130690.0,
      "end_time": 134213.0,
      "text": "You can think of teaming as a kind of pickup game in the park,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 134237.0,
      "end_time": 137161.0,
      "text": "in contrast to the formal, well-practiced team."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 137185.0,
      "end_time": 139713.0,
      "text": "Now, which one is going to win in a playoff?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 139737.0,
      "end_time": 141333.0,
      "text": "The answer is obvious."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 141828.0,
      "end_time": 143692.0,
      "text": "So why do I study teaming?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 144550.0,
      "end_time": 148972.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s because it&#39;s the way more and more of us have to work today."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 149368.0,
      "end_time": 153295.0,
      "text": "With 24/7 global fast-paced operations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 153319.0,
      "end_time": 156300.0,
      "text": "crazy shifting schedules"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 156550.0,
      "end_time": 158771.0,
      "text": "and ever-narrower expertise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 158795.0,
      "end_time": 162240.0,
      "text": "more and more of us have to work with different people all the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 162490.0,
      "end_time": 163412.0,
      "text": "to get our work done."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 163436.0,
      "end_time": 166700.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t have the luxury of stable teams."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 166940.0,
      "end_time": 170224.0,
      "text": "Now, when you can have that luxury, by all means do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 170248.0,
      "end_time": 172992.0,
      "text": "But increasingly for a lot of the work we do today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 173160.0,
      "end_time": 174474.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t have that option."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 174498.0,
      "end_time": 177350.0,
      "text": "One place where this is true is hospitals."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 177831.0,
      "end_time": 180935.0,
      "text": "This is where I&#39;ve done a lot of my research over the years."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 180959.0,
      "end_time": 185801.0,
      "text": "So it turns out hospitals have to be open 24/7."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 186524.0,
      "end_time": 189964.0,
      "text": "And patients -- well, they&#39;re all different."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 189988.0,
      "end_time": 192745.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re all different in complicated and unique ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 192769.0,
      "end_time": 198372.0,
      "text": "The average hospitalized patient is seen by 60 or so different caregivers"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 198396.0,
      "end_time": 199847.0,
      "text": "throughout his stay."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 200555.0,
      "end_time": 203238.0,
      "text": "They come from different shifts, different specialties,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 203262.0,
      "end_time": 207203.0,
      "text": "different areas of expertise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 207227.0,
      "end_time": 209720.0,
      "text": "and they may not even know each other&#39;s name."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 209744.0,
      "end_time": 213299.0,
      "text": "But they have to coordinate in order for the patient to get great care."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 213323.0,
      "end_time": 216500.0,
      "text": "And when they don&#39;t, the results can be tragic."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 216885.0,
      "end_time": 220677.0,
      "text": "Of course, in teaming, the stakes aren&#39;t always life and death."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 220701.0,
      "end_time": 224741.0,
      "text": "Consider what it takes to create an animated film,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 224765.0,
      "end_time": 226459.0,
      "text": "an award-winning animated film."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 226484.0,
      "end_time": 229640.0,
      "text": "I had the good fortune to go to Disney Animation"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 229664.0,
      "end_time": 234601.0,
      "text": "and study over 900 scientists, artists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 234626.0,
      "end_time": 237130.0,
      "text": "storytellers, computer scientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 237370.0,
      "end_time": 241000.0,
      "text": "as they teamed up in constantly changing configurations"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 241240.0,
      "end_time": 244342.0,
      "text": "to create amazing outcomes like \"Frozen.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 244366.0,
      "end_time": 248805.0,
      "text": "They just work together, and never the same group twice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 248829.0,
      "end_time": 251151.0,
      "text": "not knowing what&#39;s going to happen next."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 251175.0,
      "end_time": 254666.0,
      "text": "Now, taking care of patients in the emergency room"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 254690.0,
      "end_time": 257128.0,
      "text": "and designing an animated film"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 257152.0,
      "end_time": 259440.0,
      "text": "are obviously very different work."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 259464.0,
      "end_time": 263200.0,
      "text": "Yet underneath the differences, they have a lot in common."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 263224.0,
      "end_time": 266623.0,
      "text": "You have to get different expertise at different times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 266647.0,
      "end_time": 270171.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t have fixed roles, you don&#39;t have fixed deliverables,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 270196.0,
      "end_time": 273734.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re going to be doing a lot of things that have never been done before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 273758.0,
      "end_time": 276219.0,
      "text": "and you can&#39;t do it in a stable team."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 276776.0,
      "end_time": 280363.0,
      "text": "Now, this way of working isn&#39;t easy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 280387.0,
      "end_time": 283939.0,
      "text": "but as I said, it&#39;s more and more the way many of us have to work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 283963.0,
      "end_time": 285360.0,
      "text": "so we have to understand it."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 285384.0,
      "end_time": 288994.0,
      "text": "And I would argue that it&#39;s especially needed"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 289180.0,
      "end_time": 291123.0,
      "text": "for work that&#39;s complex and unpredictable"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 291148.0,
      "end_time": 293149.0,
      "text": "and for solving big problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 293173.0,
      "end_time": 296972.0,
      "text": "Paul Polman, the Unilever CEO, put this really well"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 296996.0,
      "end_time": 301120.0,
      "text": "when he said, \"The issues we face today are so big and so challenging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 301144.0,
      "end_time": 303516.0,
      "text": "it becomes quite clear we can&#39;t do it alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 303540.0,
      "end_time": 307531.0,
      "text": "and so there is a certain humility in knowing you have to invite people in.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 307943.0,
      "end_time": 314109.0,
      "text": "Issues like food or water scarcity cannot be done by individuals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 314134.0,
      "end_time": 315732.0,
      "text": "even by single companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 315756.0,
      "end_time": 317332.0,
      "text": "even by single sectors."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 317356.0,
      "end_time": 322496.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re reaching out to team across big teaming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 322520.0,
      "end_time": 324190.0,
      "text": "grand-scale teaming."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 324591.0,
      "end_time": 326804.0,
      "text": "Take the quest for smart cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 327342.0,
      "end_time": 329926.0,
      "text": "Maybe you&#39;ve seen some of the rhetoric:"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 329951.0,
      "end_time": 333525.0,
      "text": "mixed-use designs, zero net energy buildings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 333549.0,
      "end_time": 335834.0,
      "text": "smart mobility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 335858.0,
      "end_time": 338353.0,
      "text": "green, livable, wonderful cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 339162.0,
      "end_time": 342354.0,
      "text": "We have the vocabulary, we have the visions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 342379.0,
      "end_time": 344268.0,
      "text": "not to mention the need."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 344292.0,
      "end_time": 345787.0,
      "text": "We have the technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 345812.0,
      "end_time": 347299.0,
      "text": "Two megatrends --"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 347323.0,
      "end_time": 350229.0,
      "text": "urbanization, we&#39;re fast becoming a more urban planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 350254.0,
      "end_time": 351554.0,
      "text": "and climate change --"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 351578.0,
      "end_time": 354440.0,
      "text": "have been increasingly pointing to cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 354464.0,
      "end_time": 356718.0,
      "text": "as a crucial target for innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 357106.0,
      "end_time": 359376.0,
      "text": "And now around the world in various locations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 359400.0,
      "end_time": 361388.0,
      "text": "people have been teaming up"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 361412.0,
      "end_time": 365623.0,
      "text": "to design and try to create green, livable, smart cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 366154.0,
      "end_time": 368654.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a massive innovation challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 369362.0,
      "end_time": 371580.0,
      "text": "To understand it better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 371820.0,
      "end_time": 376590.0,
      "text": "I studied a start-up -- a smart-city software start-up --"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 376614.0,
      "end_time": 379268.0,
      "text": "as it teamed up with a real estate developer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 379292.0,
      "end_time": 381270.0,
      "text": "some civil engineers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 381295.0,
      "end_time": 382752.0,
      "text": "a mayor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 383680.0,
      "end_time": 387539.0,
      "text": "an architect, some builders, some tech companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 387563.0,
      "end_time": 391837.0,
      "text": "Their goal was to build a demo smart city from scratch."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 392475.0,
      "end_time": 396986.0,
      "text": "OK. Five years into the project, not a whole lot had happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 397100.0,
      "end_time": 401359.0,
      "text": "Six years, still no ground broken."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 401383.0,
      "end_time": 404698.0,
      "text": "It seemed that teaming across industry boundaries"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 404722.0,
      "end_time": 407340.0,
      "text": "was really, really hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 408215.0,
      "end_time": 409426.0,
      "text": "OK, so ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 410362.0,
      "end_time": 413838.0,
      "text": "We had inadvertently discovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 413862.0,
      "end_time": 417366.0,
      "text": "what I call \"professional culture clash\" with this project."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 417390.0,
      "end_time": 421449.0,
      "text": "You know, software engineers and real estate developers"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 421473.0,
      "end_time": 423660.0,
      "text": "think differently --"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 423900.0,
      "end_time": 424847.0,
      "text": "really differently:"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 424872.0,
      "end_time": 429213.0,
      "text": "different values, different time frames -- time frames is a big one --"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 429237.0,
      "end_time": 432394.0,
      "text": "and different jargon, different language."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 432418.0,
      "end_time": 435850.0,
      "text": "And so they don&#39;t always see eye to eye."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 435109.0,
      "end_time": 439104.0,
      "text": "I think this is a bigger problem than most of us realize."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 439128.0,
      "end_time": 443732.0,
      "text": "In fact, I think professional culture clash"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 443756.0,
      "end_time": 448256.0,
      "text": "is a major barrier to building the future that we aspire to build."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 448280.0,
      "end_time": 451610.0,
      "text": "And so it becomes a problem that we have to understand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 451850.0,
      "end_time": 455170.0,
      "text": "a problem that we have to figure out how to crack."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 455410.0,
      "end_time": 459880.0,
      "text": "So how do you make sure teaming goes well, especially big teaming?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 459819.0,
      "end_time": 463930.0,
      "text": "This is the question I&#39;ve been trying to solve for a number of years"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 463117.0,
      "end_time": 464572.0,
      "text": "in many different workplaces"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 464596.0,
      "end_time": 465877.0,
      "text": "with my research."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 466266.0,
      "end_time": 470446.0,
      "text": "Now, to begin to get just a glimpse of the answer to this question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 470470.0,
      "end_time": 471782.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s go back to Chile."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 472403.0,
      "end_time": 477469.0,
      "text": "In Chile, we witnessed 10 weeks of teaming"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 477493.0,
      "end_time": 479654.0,
      "text": "by hundreds of individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 479678.0,
      "end_time": 482236.0,
      "text": "from different professions, different companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 482260.0,
      "end_time": 484721.0,
      "text": "different sectors, even different nations."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 484745.0,
      "end_time": 488128.0,
      "text": "And as this process unfolded,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 488152.0,
      "end_time": 492762.0,
      "text": "they had lots of ideas, they tried many things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 492786.0,
      "end_time": 495360.0,
      "text": "they experimented, they failed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 495600.0,
      "end_time": 498558.0,
      "text": "they experienced devastating daily failure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 498582.0,
      "end_time": 500305.0,
      "text": "but they picked up, persevered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 500329.0,
      "end_time": 502413.0,
      "text": "and went on forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 502437.0,
      "end_time": 507660.0,
      "text": "And really, what we witnessed there"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 507900.0,
      "end_time": 509724.0,
      "text": "was they were able to be humble"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 509748.0,
      "end_time": 513610.0,
      "text": "in the face of the very real challenge ahead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 513850.0,
      "end_time": 515360.0,
      "text": "curious -- all of these diverse individuals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 515384.0,
      "end_time": 518870.0,
      "text": "diverse expertise especially, nationality as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 518111.0,
      "end_time": 520481.0,
      "text": "were quite curious about what each other brings."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 520505.0,
      "end_time": 524956.0,
      "text": "And they were willing to take risks to learn fast what might work."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 524980.0,
      "end_time": 530206.0,
      "text": "And ultimately, 17 days into this remarkable story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 530230.0,
      "end_time": 531971.0,
      "text": "ideas came from everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 531995.0,
      "end_time": 535473.0,
      "text": "They came from Andr√© Sougarret, who is a brilliant mining engineer"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 535497.0,
      "end_time": 538204.0,
      "text": "who was appointed by the government to lead the rescue."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 538229.0,
      "end_time": 539871.0,
      "text": "They came from NASA."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 539895.0,
      "end_time": 542467.0,
      "text": "They came from Chilean Special Forces."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 543700.0,
      "end_time": 545331.0,
      "text": "They came from volunteers around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 545355.0,
      "end_time": 549646.0,
      "text": "And while many of us, including myself, watched from afar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 550273.0,
      "end_time": 554342.0,
      "text": "these folks made slow, painful progress through the rock."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 554366.0,
      "end_time": 558370.0,
      "text": "On the 17th day, they broke through to the refuge."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 558394.0,
      "end_time": 560346.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just a remarkable moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 560905.0,
      "end_time": 565448.0,
      "text": "And with just a very small incision, they were able to find it"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 565472.0,
      "end_time": 567667.0,
      "text": "through a bunch of experimental techniques."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 567691.0,
      "end_time": 570160.0,
      "text": "And then for the next 53 days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 570184.0,
      "end_time": 574338.0,
      "text": "that narrow lifeline would be the path"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 574362.0,
      "end_time": 578356.0,
      "text": "where food and medicine and communication would travel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 578380.0,
      "end_time": 582446.0,
      "text": "while aboveground, for 53 more days, they continued the teaming"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 582470.0,
      "end_time": 586295.0,
      "text": "to find a way to create a much larger hole"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 586319.0,
      "end_time": 589755.0,
      "text": "and also to design a capsule."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 589779.0,
      "end_time": 590968.0,
      "text": "This is the capsule."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 590992.0,
      "end_time": 593233.0,
      "text": "And then on the 69th day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 593257.0,
      "end_time": 596410.0,
      "text": "over 22 painstaking hours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 596660.0,
      "end_time": 599252.0,
      "text": "they managed to pull the miners out one by one."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 599276.0,
      "end_time": 602351.0,
      "text": "So how did they overcome professional culture clash?"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 602375.0,
      "end_time": 606778.0,
      "text": "I would say in a word, it&#39;s leadership, but let me be more specific."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 606802.0,
      "end_time": 608723.0,
      "text": "When teaming works,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 608747.0,
      "end_time": 611579.0,
      "text": "you can be sure that some leaders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 611604.0,
      "end_time": 612999.0,
      "text": "leaders at all levels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 613230.0,
      "end_time": 616304.0,
      "text": "have been crystal clear that they don&#39;t have the answers."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 616328.0,
      "end_time": 618665.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s call this \"situational humility.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 618689.0,
      "end_time": 619988.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s appropriate humility."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 620120.0,
      "end_time": 621604.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t know how to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 621629.0,
      "end_time": 624828.0,
      "text": "You can be sure, as I said before, people were very curious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 624852.0,
      "end_time": 626930.0,
      "text": "and this situational humility"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 626954.0,
      "end_time": 629114.0,
      "text": "combined with curiosity"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 629139.0,
      "end_time": 631705.0,
      "text": "creates a sense of psychological safety"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 631729.0,
      "end_time": 633748.0,
      "text": "that allows you take risks with strangers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 633772.0,
      "end_time": 637439.0,
      "text": "because let&#39;s face it: it&#39;s hard to speak up, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 637463.0,
      "end_time": 638762.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s hard to ask for help."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 638786.0,
      "end_time": 642276.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s hard to offer an idea that might be a stupid idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 642300.0,
      "end_time": 644160.0,
      "text": "if you don&#39;t know people very well."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 644400.0,
      "end_time": 646867.0,
      "text": "You need psychological safety to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 647613.0,
      "end_time": 652267.0,
      "text": "They overcame what I like to call the basic human challenge:"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 652291.0,
      "end_time": 655337.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s hard to learn if you already know."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 655361.0,
      "end_time": 658785.0,
      "text": "And unfortunately, we&#39;re hardwired to think we know."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 658809.0,
      "end_time": 662103.0,
      "text": "And so we&#39;ve got to remind ourselves -- and we can do it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 662127.0,
      "end_time": 663317.0,
      "text": "to be curious;"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 663341.0,
      "end_time": 665539.0,
      "text": "to be curious about what others bring."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 665563.0,
      "end_time": 671206.0,
      "text": "And that curiosity can also spawn a kind of generosity of interpretation."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 671830.0,
      "end_time": 674904.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s another barrier, and you all know it."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 674928.0,
      "end_time": 677326.0,
      "text": "You wouldn&#39;t be in this room if you didn&#39;t know it."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 677350.0,
      "end_time": 680785.0,
      "text": "And to explain it, I&#39;m going to quote from the movie \"The Paper Chase.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 680809.0,
      "end_time": 682826.0,
      "text": "This, by the way, is what Hollywood thinks"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 682850.0,
      "end_time": 684966.0,
      "text": "a Harvard professor is supposed to look like."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 684990.0,
      "end_time": 686248.0,
      "text": "You be the judge."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 686272.0,
      "end_time": 688282.0,
      "text": "The professor in this famous scene,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 688306.0,
      "end_time": 691368.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s welcoming the new 1L class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 691392.0,
      "end_time": 693861.0,
      "text": "and he says, \"Look to your left. Look to your right."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 693885.0,
      "end_time": 695607.0,
      "text": "one of you won&#39;t be here next year.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 695631.0,
      "end_time": 698521.0,
      "text": "What message did they hear? \"It&#39;s me or you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 699300.0,
      "end_time": 701358.0,
      "text": "For me to succeed, you must fail."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 701383.0,
      "end_time": 705892.0,
      "text": "Now, I don&#39;t think too many organizations welcome newcomers that way anymore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 705916.0,
      "end_time": 710927.0,
      "text": "but still, many times people arrive with that message of scarcity anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 710951.0,
      "end_time": 712348.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s me or you."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 712372.0,
      "end_time": 716948.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s awfully hard to team if you inadvertently see others as competitors."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 716972.0,
      "end_time": 719295.0,
      "text": "So we have to overcome that one as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 719319.0,
      "end_time": 722961.0,
      "text": "and when we do, the results can be awesome."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 723450.0,
      "end_time": 725394.0,
      "text": "Abraham Lincoln said once,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 725418.0,
      "end_time": 729300.0,
      "text": "\"I don&#39;t like that man very much. I must get to know him better.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 729827.0,
      "end_time": 730978.0,
      "text": "Think about that --"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 731200.0,
      "end_time": 733743.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t like him, that means I don&#39;t know him well enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 733768.0,
      "end_time": 734919.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s extraordinary."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 734943.0,
      "end_time": 736616.0,
      "text": "This is the mindset, I have to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 736640.0,
      "end_time": 740370.0,
      "text": "this is the mindset you need for effective teaming."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 741285.0,
      "end_time": 743826.0,
      "text": "In our silos, we can get things done."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 743850.0,
      "end_time": 747235.0,
      "text": "But when we step back and reach out and reach across,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 747259.0,
      "end_time": 749302.0,
      "text": "miracles can happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 749326.0,
      "end_time": 751157.0,
      "text": "Miners can be rescued,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 751181.0,
      "end_time": 752624.0,
      "text": "patients can be saved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 752648.0,
      "end_time": 755565.0,
      "text": "beautiful films can be created."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 756650.0,
      "end_time": 758786.0,
      "text": "To get there, I think there&#39;s no better advice than this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 758810.0,
      "end_time": 761360.0,
      "text": "look to your left, look to your right."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 761610.0,
      "end_time": 767110.0,
      "text": "How quickly can you find the unique talents, skills"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 767350.0,
      "end_time": 768486.0,
      "text": "and hopes of your neighbor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 768510.0,
      "end_time": 771979.0,
      "text": "and how quickly, in turn, can you convey what you bring?"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 772300.0,
      "end_time": 776336.0,
      "text": "Because for us to team up to build the future we know we can create"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 776360.0,
      "end_time": 777869.0,
      "text": "that none of us can do alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 777893.0,
      "end_time": 779475.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s the mindset we need."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 779831.0,
      "end_time": 781122.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 781146.0,
      "end_time": 784895.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}